name: owslib
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.26.0" %}

package:
  name: owslib
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/O/OWSLib/OWSLib-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8c4cb06338eb6405c2aeced0b6d085682aa61f0f2e528f1c788d68dc50df941b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - pyproj <3.3.0
    - python-dateutil >=1.5
    - pytz
    - pyyaml
    - requests >=1.0

test:
  imports:
    - owslib
    - owslib.coverage
    - owslib.feature
    - owslib.swe
    - owslib.swe.observation
    - owslib.swe.sensor
    - owslib.waterml
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://geopython.github.io/OWSLib
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: OGC Web Service utility library

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kalxas
    - tomkralidis
    - pelson
    - ocefpaf
